    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>In former classifications, referred to a major division of Mammalia comprising all hoofed mammals, which are now divided into the orders Perissodactyla (odd-toed ungulates) and Artiodactyla (even-toed ungulates).</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
